Let’s first make a pairs plots of the data

pairs(airquality)

Here’s a regretion model of ozone and wind, solar radiation, and temperature.

library(stats)
fit <- lm(Ozone ~Wind + Solar.R + Temp, data = airquality)
summary(fit)

Let’s first simulate some data.
